data.description: You will enjoy coming home to this spacious 3/2.5 home in the La Hiki neighborhood of Mehana in Kapolei. Central air is powered by 23 PV panels grandfathered into a NEM contract, your bill stays low all year long. This home features an enclosed garage for 2 cars and room in the driveway for more. The owners installed decking around the home for easy outdoor maintenance and enjoyment of your large backyard. There is laminate flooring throughout the main level of the home for easy cleaning and an open floor plan creates a cool and uncongested space. You will find all 3 bedrooms on the 2nd level of the home, as well as the primary and secondary full bathrooms and wall to wall carpeting. This home has been very well maintained and cared for by the original owners. Home is being sold as is. Located in close proximity to Ho'okele Elementary, Kapolei Middle and High Schools and UH West Oahu, as well as shopping, dining, entertainment and freeway access. Viewing of home through open houses on Sundays only.
